        "text": "These actors have decided nudity is a no-no.\n\nNudity in television and film is more common than ever before. That doesn't mean just anyone will do it, however.\n\nMany of today's actors have very specific rules around filming nude scenes or sex scenes. If they're going to consent, there's a certain amount of comfortability and safety required.\n\nOthers see nudity as a no-go no matter what the circumstances. These celebrities have opened up about where they stand when it comes to getting naked on camera.\n\n1. Julia Roberts doesn't see the artistic value in getting naked.\n\n2. Chris Pratt was a stripper once, but he keeps his body to himself these days.\n\n3. Anna Kendrick isn't opposed to sex scenes, but she draws the line at nudity.\n\n4. Sarah Jessica Parker was the only Sex and the City cast member who said no to nudity.\n\n5. Mila Kunis will get as risque as side boob, but that's it.\n\n6. Ricky Gervais doesn't think anyone wants or needs to see it all.\n\n7. Jessica Alba said nudity isn't doing anything for the movies she's in.\n\n8. Megan Fox worries about her kids possibly seeing it one day.\n\n9. Rachel Bilson said she's almost lost out on roles over nudity.\n\n10. Samuel L. Jackson wouldn't mind a body double if necessary.\n\n11. Sarah Michelle Gellar may have decided against nudity after feeling uncomfortable with what she was asked of during her Buffy years.\n\n12. Allison Williams was the only Girls castmate who didn't get naked.\n\n13. Keira Knightley has decided she will no longer consider nude scenes for male directors after becoming a mother in 2015.\n\n14. Jessica Simpson says no potential professional accolades will get her to change her mind about nudity.\n\n15. Neal McDonough was fired from ABC's Scoundrels for refusing sex scenes.\n\n16. Ashley Benson says no to any nudity she feels is gratuitous.\n\n17. Rebel Wilson won't consider nudity for a comedy.\n\n18. Jennifer Garner says, \"the world deserves better.\"\n\n19. Mandy Moore just thinks there are better ways to be sexy.\n\n20. Kristen Bell won't give the men of the internet what they want.\n\nWhat actors shouldn't have gotten naked for a scene? Which should have? Interested to hear what you think in the comments!\n\nShare This Article"
